      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''To my husband and to the public man, I therefore ask for a public apology, not having received one privately.''</p>
        <p>VERONICA LARIO, the wife of Silvio Berlusconi, Italy's former prime minister, in a published letter complaining about his flirtations. [A4]</p>
